T1  - Bureaucratic corruption and the rate of temptation: do wages in the civil service affect corruption, and by how much?
AU  - Van Rijckeghem, Caroline
AU  - Weder, Beatrice
JO  - Journal of Development Economics
VL  - 65
IS  - 2
SP  - 307
EP  - 331
PY  - 2001
DA  - 2001/08/01/
